headline: Will Broadcom’s Rally Continue After 80% Gain and AI Momentum in 2025?
summary: If you are wondering what to do with Broadcom stock right now, you are not alone. The past year has rewarded loyal investors handsomely, with Broadcom returning over 80% in the last 12 months. Even over shorter windows, there have been strong moves, as the stock has soared more than 26% in just the past 90 days.
